The paper discusses optimization of retrieval algorithms on large scale knowledge graphs, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories of computer science. The most likely category is cs.DB (databases), as the paper focuses on graph databases and their optimization. The paper also discusses information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI) techniques for optimizing queries on knowledge graphs. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning (cs.DL) and graph-based machine learning (cs.LG) for optimization.
